{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Okinawa Journal</strong> is a captivating point-and-click narrative game set during the summer of 2000 in the serene yet mysterious landscapes of Okinawa. You step into the ethereal role of Kami, a guardian angel tasked with guiding Haruki, a struggling journalist, as he delves into the baffling disappearance of a beloved actress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along the way, you\u2019ll meet a diverse cast of characters\u2014both human and spirit\u2014each harboring their own secrets, ambitions, and obligations. As the investigation unfolds, you\u2019ll uncover a web of hidden truths tied to Okinawa\u2019s dark past, with consequences that linger in the present.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With challenging decisions, intriguing locations to explore, and multiple endings to discover, <strong>Okinawa Journal</strong> invites you to shape a story where every choice carries weight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/SteamPageTitles_HarukisInsight.png?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/GIF_NorthCourtyard.gif?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With Haruki's Insight, you'll always know what still interests him. Also, Okinawa Journal is a succinctly written text-based game. There are no walls of text or meandering dialogue. The characters in the game summarize all their interactions in thought, which you, as a guardian angel, are able to understand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/SteamPageTitles_SpiritsWithMotivations.png?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/GIF_CentralExterior.gif?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll encounter spirits that have their own motivations. You can help them for a reward, or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/SteamPageTitles_ChoicesMatter.png?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/Nago_Cemetery_Choice.gif?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At certain points, you'll need to make important choices for Haruki. Some decisions may require time to think through. That's okay, though\u2014time only moves forward during an interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/extras/InteractPrompts.gif?t=1739559580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every click matters. Blindly clicking on everything could lead to unexpected consequences... or rewards.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3494660?t=1739559580","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739559580","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/095e2f7b5a7d541f84166794eaeee71d7a83d2de/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739559580","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494660/095e2f7b5a7d541f84166794eaeee71d7a83d2de/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739559580","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3504350,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Okinawa J